eplyTime":"2019-07-25T10:39:47.000Z","msg":"推哂7.26 7.27 post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7ee0c57e6a2177fe339ae54a52e27e9b5215e44","tid":1363822,"uid":50790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e87112123415d75213508acc012c7d07288f5278","tid":1363822,"uid":103230,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T08:59:47.000Z","msg":"殯殮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n集體憑弔何君堯老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T11:28:17.000Z","msg":"仲可以灑下溪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44b50c68971819b5d233b0e9f8e5c9a5fa6fbc39","tid":1363822,"uid":266503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T11:53:50.000Z","msg":"政權除了要我們恐懼多，還要散佈仇恨。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1065677\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1065677&d=9aIS%2Fhk2hxf5w8hb7WAMURvkGFRp1GVnGvdlwu1qkBE%3D&h=670543a6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1065677&h=892f01aa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1065677</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「人民不應該害怕他們的政府，政府應該害怕它的人民。」（People should not be afraid of their governments. Governments should be afraid of their people.）<br />\n<br />\n「藝術家用謊言揭露真相，政治家用謊言掩蓋真相。」（Artists use lies to tell the truth, while politicians use them to cover the truth up.）<br />\n<br />\n「沒有舞蹈的革命，是不值得發動的革命。」（A revolution without dancing is a revolution not worth having）<br />\n<br />\n「面具之下只是個血肉之軀，而在這面具之下的，還有一個理念，只不過，理念，是刀槍不入的。」（Beneath this mask there is more than flesh. Beneath this mask there is an idea, Mr.Creedy, and ideas are bulletproof..）<br />\n<br />\n「我們的尊嚴可能不值錢，但它卻是我們唯一真正擁有的東西。它是我們最後一寸領地，但在那一寸領地裡，我們是自由的。」（Our integrity sells for so little, but it is all we really have. It is the very last inch of us, but within that inch, we are free）<br />\n<br />\n「力量來自團結，團結來自信念」（Strength through unity, unity through faith）<br />\n<br />\n「恐懼往往是政府的終極武器。」（Fear became the ultimate tool of this government）<br />\n<br />\n「就算政府擁有的武力統治不讓人民發言，自由的言論仍然充滿著強大的力量。」（the truncheon may be used in lieu of conversation, words will always retain their power)"},{"pid":"074c87c0789f3bd85c43903075a00de7cfba31f1","tid":1363822,"uid":38833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T12:05:13.000Z","msg":"記得去街市買埋平價燒味飯 唔係一陣餓親個肚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實好多人平時黎元朗買餸嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1364551/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1364551/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"99a6a1befae08174669c28b3f1c8dad5161a833e","tid":1363822,"uid":29675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T12:10:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>記得去街市買埋平價燒味飯 唔係一陣餓親個肚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96126765f3ec924a18786eb6d783e786eaf8a453","tid":1363822,"uid":38218,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"a3c07c1556fb85480f1740ca26202945ef4caeeb","tid":1363822,"uid":75664,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T08:50:25.000Z","msg":"教育<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n教啲鄉黑點做人"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T12:18:51.000Z","msg":"其實我好反感去&quot;悼念&quot;李鵬<br />\n雖則我係90後<br />\n無親身經歷當年64<br />\n明白個活動用意<br />\n但改改個標題做：屠夫李鵬反思會<br />\n籍此<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">教育</span></span></strong>大眾當年條友點樣段送一個國土的未來<br />\n亦同樣可以符合聚集的條件"},{"pid":"a2f2129ff6e7bd45ff1a883f5ef78ddf8d476d5e","tid":1363822,"uid":12773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score"